$ ASM striping
@ striping

The purpose of *ASM striping* is twofold:
  • Balance load accross all → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/Automatic-Storage-Management/disk[ASM disks]
  • Reduce latency for certain file types

Stripe size:
  • The *fine grained* stripe size is always 128 KB.
  • The *coarse grained* stripe size is equal to a → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/database/files/Automatic-Storage-Management/allocation-unit
